snippet.title: Gameboy Longplay [169] Duck Tales 2
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Ravenlord

DuckTales 2 is a platform video game developed and published by Capcom and is a sequel to the original DuckTales based on the Disney animated series of the same name. Originally released on the Nintendo Entertainment System in early 1993, the title was later ported to the Game Boy handheld system in Japan and North America at the end of the year. -
